<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","textColor":"white","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<h2 class="has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size">代理进口服务</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","textColor":"white","fontSize":"small"} -->
<h2 class="has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color has-small-font-size">Agent import service</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#b0976d"}},"fontSize":"small"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="color:#b0976d">一站式品质高端代理原装进口服务</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:themepark-block/themepark-wright {"font2":28} -->
<div class="wp-block-themepark-block-themepark-wright content-super-p" style="font-size:12px;line-height:28px;padding:10px 10px;"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"14px"}},"textColor":"white"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color" style="font-size:14px">采购渠道不完善、渠道成本过高、采购的葡萄酒性价比不高，使红酒代进口业务在中国的发展受到制约，红酒进口委托方不能得到真正的实惠。随着进口红酒销售热度在国内的不断攀升，让委托方真正得到实惠的优质、 高效代进口服务将成为市场发展的必然趋势。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"white","fontSize":"small"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color has-small-font-size">通过在上海设立全球采购中心以及在原产地设立分支机构，在法国、智利、澳洲等红酒原产地，通过买断期酒、参股酒庄、参加拍卖会、建立从酒庄到销售一体化的红酒产销战略联盟等方式实现了对上游优质红酒货源的控制。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
